<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/544728-why-did-capote-never-wrote-something">Why did Capote never wrote something similar to &quot;A Tree of Night&quot;? Suppose no one but him could answer this. Another question would be: Did Truman really loose his ability to write after the trauma of watching the killers of &quot;In Cold Blood&quot; executions?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_544728'><a id="like_count_community_question_544728" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/544728?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">3 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F2281.The_Complete_Stories_of_Truman_Capote">like</a></span>

</li>
