<a href="/questions/544728-why-did-capote-never-wrote-something">5 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/544728-why-did-capote-never-wrote-something">See all 2 answers</a>
</li>
