<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/136309123-darlene"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1626366038i/136309123._UY100_CR16,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/136309123-darlene">Darlene</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">You are correct. Truman Capote did write a tree of night. Truman stopped writing and took to drinking more after his upper class friends turned on him<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">You are correct. Truman Capote did write a tree of night. Truman stopped writing and took to drinking more after his upper class friends turned on him for writing their secrets in a book that he was writing. It remained unfinished, but was published. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
