          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780141188089" href="/book/show/68063.The_Complete_Stories">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4452312-steven?shelf=books-i-own">books-i-own</a>, 
